OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mostly
OL,6,Fcloudy evening with a few showers
OL,7,Fmoving eastwards. It will become dry
OL,8,Fwith clear spells overnight leading to
OL,9,Fa frost in places and perhaps the odd
OL,10,Ffog patch.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA cold start to the day with
OL,13,Fa frost for some places. It will
OL,14,Fremain dry with plenty of sunshine but
OL,15,Fperhaps some high cloud spreading east
OL,16,Fin the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
